{"title_page": "All I Am (Jess Glynne song)", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = All I Am\n| cover      = All I Am (Jess Glynne).jpg\n| alt        = \n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Jess Glynne]]\n| album      = [[Always In Between]]\n| released   = 17 August 2018\n| format     = [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| recorded   = \n| genre      = [[House music|House]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Essential tracks|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/essential-tracks-wxnw7vvh6|website=The Times|accessdate=9 September 2018|date=31 August 2018}}</ref>\n| length     = 3:39\n| label      = [[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]]\n| writer     = {{hlist|[[Jess Glynne|Jessica Glynne]]|[[Jin Jin (musician)|Janee Bennett]]|[[James Newman (musician)|James Newman]]|[[Frances (musician)|Sophie Cooke]]|Bastian Langebaek|[[Sandy Rivera]]|Jay \"Sinister\" Sealee}}  \n| producer   = [[Mark Ralph (record producer)|Mark Ralph]] \n| prev_title = [[I'll Be There (Jess Glynne song)|I'll Be There]]\n| prev_year  = 2018\n| next_title = So Real (Warriors)\n| next_year  = 2018\n| misc       = {{External music video|{{YouTube|Lq6q3YJqLaQ|\"All I Am\"}}}}\n}}\n\"'''All I Am'''\" is a song by English singer-songwriter [[Jess Glynne]]. It was released through [[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]] on 17 August 2018 as the second single from her second studio album, ''[[Always In Between]]'' (2018).<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/jess-glynne-announces-new-single-all-i-am__23622/|title=Jess Glynne announces new single All I Am|last=Copsey|first=Rob|date=13 August 2018|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=4 September 2018}}</ref> It contains a sample replay of [[Kings of Tomorrow]]'s 2000 single \"Finally\" bass line performed and produced by [[Mark Summers]] of Scorccio.\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download\n| title1 = All I Am\n| length1 = 3:38\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download\n| title1 = All I Am\n| note1 = T