27120707/http://www.environ.ie/en/Heritage/NationalParksandWildlife/News/MainBody%2C5384%2Cen.htm |archivedate=27 September 2011 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FC Poster\">{{cite web |url=http://www.forestry.gov.uk/pdf/englandnweredkiteinfoposters.pdf/$FILE/englandnweredkiteinfoposters.pdf |title=Grizedale Red Kite Project |work=Forestry Commission information posters |publisher=Forestry commission |accessdate=12 July 2010}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Gambia>{{cite book |last1=Barlow |first1=C. |last2=Wacher |first2=T. |last3=Disley |first3=T. |year=1997 |title=A Field Guide to Birds of the Gambia and Senegal |publisher=Pica Press |location=Mountfield, UK |isbn=978-1-873403-32-7}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=gigrin>{{cite web |url=http://www.gigrin.co.uk |title=Red Kite Feeding Station&nbsp;\u2014 Gigrin Farm |accessdate=27 October 2006}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=goldeneagle>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldeneagle.ie/news_viewnews.php?x=3&z=44&news_id=9&article=277 |title=Golden Eagle Trust &#124; Red Kite &#124; Project Updates |publisher=Goldeneagle.ie |accessdate=28 August 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305215209/http://www.goldeneagle.ie/news_viewnews.php?x=3&z=44&news_id=9&article=277 |archivedate=5 March 2012 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Harewood>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/handsonnature/estates/harewood.shtml |title=Birder watchers' paradise |work=BBC Hands on Nature |publisher=BBC |pages=Parks: Harewood Estate |accessdate=26 October 2009}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=dofbasen>[http://www.dofbasen.dk/ART/art.php?art=02390 Danish Ornithological Society]</ref>\n\n<!--(replaced by ref name=dofbasen)<ref name=Hjembaek2009>{{cite web |first=Gert |last=Hjemb\u00e6k |url=http://www.dof.dk/index.php?id=nyheder&s=nyheder&m=visning&nyhed_id=690 |publisher=[[Dansk Ornitologisk Forening]] |title=Den r\u00f8de drage bliver h\u00e6ngende i Danmark |trans_title=The red dragon lingers in Denmark |language=da |date=25 November 2009 |accessdate=28 November 2009}